## Import

This resource **must** be imported before it can be managed. The import ID is always the fixed string `quagga_bgp`.

In Terraform v1.5.0 and later, use an [`import` block](https://developer.hashicorp.com/terraform/language/import):

```terraform
import {
  to = opnsense_quagga_bgp.settings
  id = "quagga_bgp"
}
```

Using `terraform import`:

```console
% terraform import opnsense_quagga_bgp.settings quagga_bgp
```
